OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: John
OL,4,CHaddock
OL,6,FJohn Haddock, Age 101, RAF
OL,8,FInterviewed 20 February 2024
OL,10,FA navigator who had been part of
OL,11,FCoastal Command, Mr Haddock had
OL,12,Foriginally been based on the East
OL,13,Fcoast targeting enemy traffic.
OL,15,F"We attacked, always," he said.
OL,17,F"Sometimes we went singly, but most
OL,18,Ftimes it was in a large formation. We
OL,19,Fcould be up to forty aircraft in
OL,20,Fformation.
