OL,4,CHaddock
OL,6,F"When the target was located we all
OL,7,Ftried to sink it or them."
OL,9,FJohn was moved to RAF Manston in Kent
OL,10,Fwith 143 Squadron in the lead-up to
OL,11,Fthe invasion and changed aircraft to
OL,12,Fthe Bristol Beaufighter.
OL,14,FAn effective two-man night fighter,
OL,15,Fits large size allowed the plane to
OL,16,Fcarry heavy weapons.
