OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: John
OL,4,CHaddock
OL,6,FMr Haddock, who also operated the
OL,7,Faircraft's radio, said the patrols -
OL,8,Fcodenamed Swing Gate - began in May.
OL,9,FHe and his colleagues provided
OL,10,Fcontinuous service until D-Day, in two
OL,11,Fto three-hour patrols.
OL,13,FDespite the invasion having gone ahead
OL,14,Fhe remembers the night of 6 June being
OL,15,F''just like any other patrol.''
